<html><head></head><body dir=3D"auto" style=3D"overflow-wrap: =
break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; line-break: after-white-space;"><p =
dir=3D"auto" style=3D"white-space: pre-wrap;"> Chris and Sasha,</p><p =
dir=3D"auto" style=3D"white-space: pre-wrap;">I hope you=E2=80=99re both =
doing well! Thank you so much for all the support you=E2=80=99ve =
provided with my claim for 23 Mays St, Devonport=E2=80=94it really means =
a lot. Following our chat on June 18, I wanted to share some expenses =
I=E2=80=99ve incurred due to the fire, and I=E2=80=99d love your advice =
on the next steps.</p><p dir=3D"auto" style=3D"white-space: =
pre-wrap;">Here=E2=80=99s what I=E2=80=99ve spent so far, with =
proofs/invoices attached:</p><ul dir=3D"auto"><li>$1,452 at Esplanade =
Hotel for 6 nights of temporary accommodation</li><li>$5,000 for rent =
(at $1,000 per week)</li><li>$727.38 for moving to the rental =
property</li><li>$340 for cleaning some clothes</li><li>$454.25 for sofa =
cleaning</li></ul><p dir=3D"auto" style=3D"white-space: pre-wrap;">Would =
it be possible to get these reimbursed under my contents and house =
insurance? I=E2=80=99d also be grateful if you could let me know if the =
distress fund (up to $3,000 as per the policy) might be available, given =
how challenging this has been.</p><p dir=3D"auto" style=3D"white-space: =
pre-wrap;">On another note, I=E2=80=99ve just sent Chris an email about =
some safety concerns and assessment ideas we touched on earlier. I=E2=80=99=
d really appreciate it if we could align this with the plan for both =
contents and house insurance. Could you share what=E2=80=99s next and =
perhaps a rough timeline? I=E2=80=99m looking forward to a returning to =
a normal l.</p><p dir=3D"auto" style=3D"white-space: pre-wrap;">Thanks =
again for your help, I look forward to hearing from you!</p><p =
dir=3D"auto" style=3D"white-space: pre-wrap;">Kind regards,<br>
Raffaella del Prete</p><div><br></div><div><object =
type=3D"application/x-apple-msg-attachment" width=3D"106" =
